'From Squeak2.9alpha of 13 June 2000 [latest update: #2988] on 26 November 2000 at 10:42:28 am'!"Change Set:		262CelesteAddons-dvfDate:			18 November 2000Author:			Daniel VainsencherThe addition of undo has broken the use of Celeste current by mail out changeset and the new mail out bug report. This change set replaces that mechanism."!!Celeste methodsFor: 'open-close' stamp: 'dvf 11/18/2000 17:06'!isActive	^mailDB notNil! !!Celeste class methodsFor: 'instance creation' stamp: 'dvf 11/18/2000 17:08'!current	"Answer the currently active Celeste (assuming that there's	only one Celeste open at a given time) or open a new one."	^Celeste allInstances detect: [:e | e isActive] ifNone: [self open].! !